{
  "texts": [
    "These results underscores the effectiveness of our toolkit in training and developing cost-effective RQA systems.",
    "We present LOCALRQA, a Python-based toolkit designed to help users develop novel retrievalaugemented QA systems.",
    "Different from existing frameworks such as LlamaIndex and LangChain, our toolkit features a wide collection of training algorithms, evaluation metrics, and deployment methods to help users quickly develop costeffective RQA systems.",
    "Strong results using models and training algorithms from recent research pave the way for future work to explore RQA methods in both practical and academic settings.",
    "We performed all of our experiments using a single A100 80G GPU, and investigated a large combination of model choices and training methods."
  ]
}